oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Avy Award Nomination
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson, Dale R.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Avy Awards Committee is asking all AFA members and all exotic bird enthusiasts for their assistance in helping us confirm this year's U.S. first breeding nominations. This list includes the common and scientific names of each species nominated. The date following is the hatch date of this successful breeding. If any person knows of a previous U.S. first breeding, please let us know. Send us detailed information or copies of published information to the AFA Home Office, P.O. Box 1568, Redondo Beach, CA 90278. Thank you for your assistance.1. Brown-headed Parrot Poicephalus cryptoxantbus Hatch Dec. 13, 19832. Red-faced LovebirdAgapornis pullaria Hatch Nov. 17, 19833.
